                ref="#otherwork_053"
                type="otherwork">
               <bibl xml:id="tag20">
            treatise on the drill Husbandry
        </bibl>
            </rs> published<lb/>
25 years after in 1724 espoused the ancient doctrine<lb/>
"&amp; asserted that water &amp; the Atmosphere supplied<lb/>
