- The objects to which this Philosopher directed<lb/>
his attention were great &amp; extensive - He proposed<lb/>
to himself first to give an accurate view of<lb/>
the organization of plants &amp; of their chemical<lb/>
composition 2<hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="superscript">dly</hi>. to describe &amp; analyse the<lb/>
