bare inspection to the Scientific<lb/>
            <lb/>
            <pb xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                n="37"
                xml:id="pb-37"
                facs="#i37"/>
            <lb/>
35<lb/>
farmer, as distinctly as the species of<lb/>
