            <lb/>
            <pb xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                n="38"
                xml:id="pb-38"
                facs="#i38"/>
            <lb/>
- It has been said &amp; undoubtedly<lb/>
with great truth that a <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">philosophical</hi>
            <lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">Chemist</hi> would make a very unprofitable<lb/>
