                rend="underline">substances</hi>
            <lb/>
which are subservient to their formation.<lb/>
- <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">These substances</hi> consequently<lb/>
