- When any of the vegetable organs<lb/>
are <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">long</add> acted upon by boiling water some of<lb/>
their parts are dissolved; &amp; after water<lb/>
