        </name>
            </rs> may be easily distinguished at a<lb/>
distance by the difference of the vegetation -<lb/>
the <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag430"
