in Gas The method of fermenting <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">peat</hi>
            <lb/>
- There is a very simple chemical mode of<lb/>
determining - the fermenting or decomposing powers<lb/>
of vegetable substances - |_It is directly in<lb/>
proportion to the quantity of matter that they<lb/>
contain volatile by Heat - or inversely as the<lb/>
quantity of <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
