than coaly matter in the proportion at least<lb/>
of from between 20 &amp; 30 to 1 - Rye grass<lb/>
distilled gave me in the 100 parts only 4 of coaly<lb/>
residuum. - Clover gave 7 - Peats gave from<lb/>
1/8 to 1/5 of their weight of residuum - &amp; Oak &amp;<lb/>
