dried &amp; sold &amp; is one of the most common<lb/>
articles of commerce of the Empire. -<lb/>
- Where animal Manures are applied as<lb/>
top dressing there is great reason to believe<lb/>
that will in all cases <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">be useful</hi>, in<lb/>
