        </term>
            </rs>. -<lb/>
- All Earthy substances, or Rocks occurring<lb/>
in considerable masses or beds that effervesce or<lb/>
emit copiously bubbles, when acids are poured<lb/>
upon them contain <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag591"
                ref="#chemical_010"
                type="chemical">
               <term xml:id="tag591">
                  <hi rend="underline">lime</hi>
               </term>
            </rs>. This is an invariable<lb/>
