               <name xml:id="tag857" type="person">
          M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. A Knight
        </name>
            </rs> which has thrown great<lb/>
light upon the whole of the theory<lb/>
of vegetation, &amp; with an account of<lb/>
which I shall conclude the lecture: -<lb/>
- <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
